description:
Brewster syncs your contacts to your phone’s built-in address book

“ONE OF THE 20 BEST IOS APPS” (TechCrunch)

“ONE OF THE 25 MOST DISRUPTIVE APPS” (Business Insider)

“Once in a while, a new app or service comes along that has the potential to truly change the way you use technology. Meet Brewster...” (Mashable)

------

How Brewster Works

1. Add your contacts from Facebook, Gmail, LinkedIn and more

2. Brewster brings together and merges contacts

3. Sync your Brewster contacts with iPhone contacts 
(also sync with iPad, Mac Contacts, and more)

Benefits

Full Contacts
Enriched with employment, education, social profiles, websites, birthdays, and more

Powerful Search
See who you know that lives in a city or works at a company and so much more

Always Up-to-Date
Automatically get the latest contact info for your contacts

Visual Caller ID
Large photos added to everyone for caller ID

Autocomplete
Every phone number and email address available anywhere

-----

Services included today: Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, Gmail, iPhone Contacts, Yahoo!, Foursquare, Instagram (note: iPhone Contacts plus Facebook required to sign-up)
